summary:
Thirteen years of work experience from different sectors such as the Oil and Gas industry and the Banking sector. 

In Norway I worked in the Oil and Gas industry as a Buyer, a Business Development and Marketing coordinator and Tendering coordinator. Furthermore, I have written “100% Oslo”; a travel guide about Oslo which can be purchased online and in many bookstores in The Netherlands.

In Spain I have worked several years for Barclays Bank as Manager of the International Clients department.

As a result of having worked in different countries, I speak Dutch, English, Spanish and Norwegian fluently.

I have recently relocated to The Netherlands (The Hague area) due to my husbands new job. After finally having settled down, I am now looking for a new position.
